    <h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
    <p>1. How do I purchase the games that i want? <br />
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; You can choose the games that you desired from the drop down list from different products web pages and click the&nbsp; Add to Cart product</p>
    <p>2. Can I purchase more than 1 games at a same time? <br />
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;YES, you can use the Continue Shopping button from both the Cart and Check out web pages to go back to products' pages to 
            purchase more games.</p>
    <p>3. How do I remove the games that I do not want from my cart? <br />
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You can select one items from the list box in the Cart page and click the Remove button to remove the seletected item.
            Or, you can use the Empty All button to remove all items in your cart.</p>
    <p>4. How do I cancel the orders? <br />
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You can use the Cancel Order button in the Check Out page to cancel the order and go back to the products' pages.</p>
